name: Scott
description: I am an easy-going man who loves meeting new friends. I am very social, outgoing, fun, friendly, and spontaneous. I am a drama-free woman and want to keep living my life that way. Im a very forward person and I know what I want. I enjoy all sorts of music… movies… books..I am a very loyal and understanding person. I know how to treat people as I am very kind and will never feel you upset with me. Sometimes I can be spontaneous but I hope that will not be a problem.
